{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><strong>Synesthesia</strong></p>\n<p>An interactive animation for my website's landing page, made with Javascript and Pose for React. It's a visual representation of my own <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grapheme-color_synesthesia\" title=\"Grapheme-Colour Synesthesia\">grapheme-colour Synesthesia</a> when I read and play musical scores. Each colour corresponds to a different musical note in a chord or melody, and each square's size represents each note's relative harmonic or melodic weight in the music. The animations are generated from a JSON file containing musical data.  </p>\n<p>Visit the <a href=\"https://bennmcgregor.com\" title=\"Landing Page\">site landing page</a> to click through the different animations and listen to the music that accompanies each one. All playing is my own.<br>\n</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9c5d2c6fac264281a3c5186dacf2a393/6a770/idontunderstand.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; float: left; width: 100%; max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 66.72727272727273%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"synesthesia placeholder\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/9c5d2c6fac264281a3c5186dacf2a393/e65ed/idontunderstand.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9c5d2c6fac264281a3c5186dacf2a393/aec71/idontunderstand.jpg 200w,\n/static/9c5d2c6fac264281a3c5186dacf2a393/d9ed2/idontunderstand.jpg 400w,\n/static/9c5d2c6fac264281a3c5186dacf2a393/e65ed/idontunderstand.jpg 800w,\n/static/9c5d2c6fac264281a3c5186dacf2a393/6a770/idontunderstand.jpg 1100w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Synesthesia"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/work/synesthesia/"}}